sub_doc_name: 技能実習生一覧表（技能実習日誌-別紙）
select_sql: SELECT I.Z228 AS `name`, IC.intern_class_name AS `class`, ( CASE WHEN I.intern_class_id = 4 THEN I.work_start_date WHEN I.intern_class_id = 5 THEN I.work_start_date2 WHEN I.intern_class_id = 6 THEN I.work_start_date3 END ) AS `dateS`, ( CASE WHEN I.intern_class_id = 4 THEN I.work_end_date WHEN I.intern_class_id = 5 THEN I.work_end_date2 WHEN I.intern_class_id = 6 THEN I.work_end_date3 END ) AS `dateE`, C.Z005 AS `company_name`, P.`name` AS `sekinin_name` FROM intern I INNER JOIN ( SELECT company_id, intern_class_id, code1 FROM intern I3 WHERE intern_id = @intern_id ) I2 ON I.company_id = I2.company_id AND I.intern_class_id = I2.intern_class_id AND I.code1 = I2.code1 INNER JOIN intern_class IC ON I.intern_class_id = IC.intern_class_id INNER JOIN company C ON I.company_id = C.company_id LEFT JOIN company_person P ON C.jissyuusekinin_id = P.company_person_id WHERE I.del_flg = 0 AND I.enrolled_flg < 2

SELECT CP.name_phonetic, CP.`name`,CP.class FROM company_person CP INNER JOIN company_person_office_select CP_OS ON CP.company_person_id = CP_OS.company_person_id INNER JOIN intern_company_office_select I_OS ON CP_OS.company_office_id = I_OS.company_office_id INNER JOIN intern I ON I_OS.intern_id = I.intern_id AND I.company_id = I_OS.company_id WHERE CP.P_del_flg = 0 AND I_OS.intern_id =  @intern_id AND CP.class3 = 1 GROUP BY CP.company_person_id

sub_doc_name: 軽微変更届出書-別途詳細（別紙）
select_sql: SELECT * FROM intern I INNER JOIN ( SELECT * FROM intern WHERE intern_id = @intern_id ) I2 ON I.intern_group_id = I2.intern_group_id WHERE I.del_flg = 0 AND I.enrolled_flg < 2 AND ( CASE WHEN I2.status_id BETWEEN 10 AND 16 THEN ((I.status_id BETWEEN 10 AND 16)) WHEN I2.status_id BETWEEN 17 AND 25 OR I2.status_id = 27 THEN ((I.status_id BETWEEN 17 AND 25) OR I.status_id = 27 ) WHEN I2.status_id BETWEEN 30 AND 39 OR I2.status_id = 26 THEN ((I.status_id BETWEEN 30 AND 39) OR I.status_id = 26 ) END ) ORDER BY I.entry_date, I.Z228
